contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentLabel: Kentico's Xperience Portal and SaaS: From Setup to Production
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentShortDescription: Kentico community member, Milan Lund, shares a ton of great information about his experiences deploying to Xperience by Kentico's SaaS environment. There's a couple of moving pieces to be aware of like the difference between Xperience by Kentico and the Xperience Portal. Make sure you read Milan's post!
